text: Hi.  HOw are you
Pretty good, whats going on today?
not much.  do you donate to any charities
I do, I love helping out people in need or need something to help them get going.
How about donating to Save the children?
It sounds like a great cause, can you tell me about it?
Yes, the money helps children with clothing, food and school
That all sounds wonderful, I would love to donate to that.
Howmuch do you think you can donate
I want to donate 1.50 to help the children get better lives.
That's great.  So wonderful for you to do that.
Yeah, the kids will really benefit from everyones help.
Would you like to maybe donate 1.75 instead of 1.50?
Hmm ya I can help .25 cents more.
Have you donated to this cause before?
No I havent, this is my first time hearing about it.
So glad you decided to donate.  This will really help
You are very welcome, thank you for introducing me to this great charity.
Do you think you will continue to donate to this charity
Yeah I will donate on the regular.
